00:29:11,760 --> 00:29:14,600
Joyce Rensaleer, Mergers and Acquisitions.

451
00:29:14,760 --> 00:29:17,800
Eddie Barzoon, Managing Director and...

452
00:29:18,640 --> 00:29:19,920
Real Estate.

453
00:29:20,040 --> 00:29:22,680
Pradeed Resh, Intellectual Properties.

454
00:29:23,280 --> 00:29:26,280
Christabella Andrioti, International Trade and Customs...

455
00:29:26,360 --> 00:29:27,920
EC and G-7.

456
00:29:30,360 --> 00:29:31,800
There it is, Kevin.

457
00:29:32,200 --> 00:29:33,520
The whole team.

458
00:29:34,000 --> 00:29:36,760
Welcome to Milton, Chadwick and Waters.

459
00:29:37,160 --> 00:29:39,760
So what do you think?
You can change the furniture if you Like.

460
00:29:39,880 --> 00:29:41,480
I guess it'll do.

461
00:29:41,840 --> 00:29:43,360
Until something better comes along?

462
00:29:43,440 --> 00:29:45,280
Kevin Lomax, Pam Garrety.

463
00:29:46,040 --> 00:29:47,440
Nice to meet you.

464
00:29:47,800 --> 00:29:49,920
Pam was at the Brooklyn D. A. 's office for 14 years...

465
00:29:50,000 --> 00:29:52,800
so she knows her way around the local scene.

466
00:29:52,960 --> 00:29:55,120
You'll expedite his bar application?

467
00:29:55,200 --> 00:29:58,400
It's in the pipeline.
For now, you'll work pro hac vice.

468
00:29:58,480 --> 00:30:01,000
I petitioned Florida for a Letter of good conduct.

469
00:30:01,080 --> 00:30:05,080
And I prepared, at Mr. Milton's request,
an overview of the Moyez case.

470
00:30:05,480 --> 00:30:06,520
The Moyez case?

471
00:30:08,320 --> 00:30:09,800
Move, move, move!

472
00:30:31,240 --> 00:30:32,640
What do you think?

473
00:30:32,720 --> 00:30:35,320
It's a health code case and it's a Loser.

474
00:30:37,560 --> 00:30:39,080
So what's the point?

475
00:30:39,800 --> 00:30:43,080
He wants to see if I'll plea-bargain.
It's a test, right?

476
00:30:44,160 --> 00:30:45,560
Isn't everything?

477
00:30:47,800 --> 00:30:50,360
It's an 18th-century Italian silk damask...

478
00:30:50,440 --> 00:30:54,560
with an embossed floriated pattern
of undulating acanthus leaves.

479
00:30:54,720 --> 00:30:56,160
Lovely, isn't it?

480
00:30:58,000 --> 00:31:00,120
And this is about what?

481
00:31:00,480 --> 00:31:01,560
The price?

482
00:31:02,280 --> 00:31:04,800
It's about $2,000 a panel.

483
00:31:06,040 --> 00:31:07,400
We'll take it...

484
00:31:08,040 --> 00:31:09,280
at $1, 400.

485
00:31:09,480 --> 00:31:11,200
You made it.

486
00:31:13,080 --> 00:31:15,360
I thought you said it was impossible.

487
00:31:15,440 --> 00:31:17,720
I thought you said it was important.

488
00:31:25,840 --> 00:31:27,480
Go get them, man.

489
00:31:27,560 --> 00:31:29,880
Tell him, ''Cut that shit down!''

490
00:31:30,200 --> 00:31:33,200
I know what they're doing over there! That's right!

491
00:31:34,280 --> 00:31:37,080
Tell him, ''Take all that noise back to Africa. ''

492
00:31:47,120 --> 00:31:49,880
Good afternoon.
I'm Looking for Phillipe Moyez.

493
00:32:02,600 --> 00:32:05,160
Look, I'm not sure I'm making myself clear.

494
00:32:05,240 --> 00:32:08,240
Moyez, you need him? To speak with him?

495
00:32:08,960 --> 00:32:10,520
Show him your boots.

496
00:32:13,000 --> 00:32:15,680
You're saying he's down here in the basement?

497
00:32:16,320 --> 00:32:17,400
In the dark?

498
00:32:17,480 --> 00:32:19,640
Where do you think I'm taking you?

499
00:32:29,920 --> 00:32:32,040
I thought I would recognize you...

500
00:32:34,080 --> 00:32:35,400
but I do not.

501
00:32:37,040 --> 00:32:38,120
Mr. Moyez?

502
00:32:40,360 --> 00:32:41,880
We've never met.

503
00:32:42,720 --> 00:32:45,040
I'm Kevin Lomax. I'm a Lawyer.

504
00:32:46,200 --> 00:32:48,040
I'm here about the animals.

505
00:32:49,800 --> 00:32:52,560
We have an investment in blood.

506
00:32:54,560 --> 00:32:56,840
Think of it as spiritual currency.

507
00:32:58,640 --> 00:33:00,400
''Spiritual currency. ''

508
00:33:02,720 --> 00:33:05,920
Look, Mr. Moyez, I'm going to need your help with this.

509
00:33:11,080 --> 00:33:13,080
What is the name of the man...

510
00:33:13,160 --> 00:33:14,920
who will prosecute us?

511
00:33:15,960 --> 00:33:17,000
Merto.

512
00:33:17,480 --> 00:33:20,200
Assistant District Attorney Arnold Merto.

513
00:33:25,640 --> 00:33:27,600
What are you doing, Mr. Moyez?

514
00:33:28,080 --> 00:33:31,000
With this tongue, we create silence.

515
00:33:31,480 --> 00:33:32,760
You can go now.

516
00:33:33,080 --> 00:33:35,000
You will have all the help...

517
00:33:35,200 --> 00:33:36,680
I can give you...

518
00:33:37,360 --> 00:33:39,360
against Monsieur Merto.

519
00:33:47,240 --> 00:33:49,560
It's arbor green. What do you think?

520
00:33:50,680 --> 00:33:52,400
Not with your complexion.

521
00:33:56,920 --> 00:33:58,920
New York City health codes.

522
00:33:59,600 --> 00:34:00,680
That's all of it?

523
00:34:00,760 --> 00:34:01,960
Not quite.

524
00:34:06,960 --> 00:34:08,240
Thanks.

525
00:34:12,560 --> 00:34:14,000
Caribbean green.

526
00:34:14,800 --> 00:34:16,960
Something cooler, maybe. Cooler.

527
00:34:17,120 --> 00:34:18,440
A cooler green.

