Overrated.

2117
02:11:37,720 --> 02:11:38,680
Biochemically...

2118
02:11:38,760 --> 02:11:43,240
no different than eating large quantities of chocolate.

2119
02:11:45,080 --> 02:11:48,640
In two minutes you won't be thinking
about Mary Ann ever again.

2120
02:11:48,920 --> 02:11:50,160
Come here.

2121
02:11:51,760 --> 02:11:53,880
She's right, my son.

2122
02:12:00,680 --> 02:12:04,440
It's time to step up and take what's yours.

2123
02:12:09,360 --> 02:12:10,600
You're right.

2124
02:12:13,000 --> 02:12:14,440
It's time.

2125
02:12:15,000 --> 02:12:16,760
Free will, right?

2126
02:12:22,000 --> 02:12:23,160
No!

2127
02:12:37,240 --> 02:12:38,760
Damn you!

2128
02:12:42,040 --> 02:12:44,040
Enough!

2129
02:12:45,960 --> 02:12:48,560
Haven't I given enough?

2130
02:13:52,520 --> 02:13:54,040
It was a nice run.

2131
02:13:54,280 --> 02:13:56,280
Had to close out someday.

2132
02:13:57,120 --> 02:13:58,720
Nobody wins them all.

2133
02:14:48,240 --> 02:14:50,320
What are you doing, baby?

2134
02:14:52,360 --> 02:14:53,720
Are you okay?

2135
02:14:56,760 --> 02:14:58,360
I am now.

2136
02:15:02,000 --> 02:15:03,600
All rise.

2137
02:15:04,040 --> 02:15:07,080
The Honorable Judge Garson Deeds presiding.

2138
02:15:10,040 --> 02:15:11,520
Please be seated.

2139
02:15:15,600 --> 02:15:18,280
You're still under oath, young lady.

2140
02:15:21,400 --> 02:15:22,680
Your witness.

2141
02:15:34,560 --> 02:15:36,040
Mr. Lomax?

2142
02:15:40,720 --> 02:15:41,920
Your Honor...

2143
02:15:43,720 --> 02:15:45,760
I'm terribly sorry.

2144
02:15:47,080 --> 02:15:49,560
But I can no longer represent my client.

2145
02:15:52,120 --> 02:15:54,360
I need to be replaced as counsel.

2146
02:15:54,440 --> 02:15:56,600
Order. Order! Order!

2147
02:15:57,600 --> 02:15:59,400
I adjourn this court.

2148
02:15:59,800 --> 02:16:03,360
This is outrageous. Are you aware of
the consequences of this action?

2149
02:16:03,440 --> 02:16:04,640
I am, sir.

2150
02:16:04,800 --> 02:16:08,400
I want to see both attorneys in my chambers immediately.

2151
02:16:08,600 --> 02:16:12,400
I'm going to adjourn this trial until
9 a. m. tomorrow morning.

2152
02:16:13,600 --> 02:16:15,280
I trusted you to defend me.

2153
02:16:15,400 --> 02:16:17,640
You swore you would! You'll burn for this!

2154
02:16:17,720 --> 02:16:20,440
You just made the biggest mistake of your life!

2155
02:16:21,480 --> 02:16:23,480
Baby, what are you doing?

2156
02:16:26,800 --> 02:16:28,320
The right thing.

2157
02:16:29,120 --> 02:16:30,800
I think the right thing.

2158
02:16:34,760 --> 02:16:35,840
Here they are.

2159
02:16:35,920 --> 02:16:37,920
- Are you gonna be disbarred?
- I don't know.

2160
02:16:38,000 --> 02:16:40,760
- How's it feel to Lose your first case?
- No comment.

2161
02:16:40,840 --> 02:16:44,840
Ain't it better to talk to them all at once?
Press conference tomorrow?

2162
02:16:45,000 --> 02:16:48,360
He ain't going to talk to you now.
Eight o'clock tomorrow morning.

2163
02:16:48,440 --> 02:16:49,800
That's it.

2164
02:16:49,960 --> 02:16:51,720
This is the story you dreamed about.

2165
02:16:51,800 --> 02:16:54,320
- There is no story.
- Bullshit.

2166
02:16:54,520 --> 02:16:57,920
A Lawyer with a crisis of conscience?
You gotta be kidding. It's huge!

2167
02:16:58,000 --> 02:17:00,840
They're going to disbar me.
Write about that.

2168
02:17:01,840 --> 02:17:04,000
Wait a second. Can they do that?

2169
02:17:04,200 --> 02:17:05,720
Not when I get through with the story.

2170
02:17:05,800 --> 02:17:08,160
You got to give me an exclusive.

2171
02:17:08,320 --> 02:17:12,200
This is wire service. This is ''60 Minutes''.

2172
02:17:12,360 --> 02:17:15,800
This is a story that needs to be told. It's you.

2173
02:17:16,160 --> 02:17:17,680
You're a star.

2174
02:17:21,520 --> 02:17:22,840
Baby.

2175
02:17:25,160 --> 02:17:26,880
Call me in the morning.

2176
02:17:27,520 --> 02:17:30,160
You got it. First thing.

2177
02:17:39,880 --> 02:17:41,200
Vanity...

2178
02:17:41,680 --> 02:17:43,920
definitely my favorite sin.

